        "title": "Jewish people scared to join Bondi inquiry, former royal commissioner says",
        "content": {
          "descriptor": {
            "type": "tagname",
            "key": "div",
            "props": {},
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "tagname",
                "key": "@@standfirst",
                "props": {},
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "content": "Ronald Sackville who led the disability royal commission says it is unlikely the the Royal Commission on Antisemitism and Social Cohesion can properly examine the experiences of Jewish Australians before its December 2026 deadline."
